column5: Was a nice day for getting out despite the slow bite. Somebody's girlfriend decided to show us oldtimers up and catch some nice jumbos.   All that really matters was we had fun
Thanks for the report Bruce Sounds like an enjoyable day spent along the water! Thanks for sharing Jacques
Great to see you were able to get some fish Bruce, we didn't do so well on Sat.
she seems to be having all the good luck which means she will keep coming out fishing with me
